{"tid":164812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老鼠入屋咬爛電線 一家四口逼居百呎廚廁相連","createTime":"2017-03-21T02:35:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T05:57:44.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e473aac41f5d3b32e4abb9040b3523140b93e67a","tid":164812,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:35:51.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>老鼠入屋咬爛電線 一家四口逼居百呎廚廁相連<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/時事要聞/article/20170320/2_488605_0/-N無悲慘世界-老鼠入屋咬爛電線-一家四口逼居百呎廚廁相連-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20170320%2F2_488605_0%2F-N%E7%84%A1%E6%82%B2%E6%85%98%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C-%E8%80%81%E9%BC%A0%E5%85%A5%E5%B1%8B%E5%92%AC%E7%88%9B%E9%9B%BB%E7%B7%9A-%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%B6%E5%9B%9B%E5%8F%A3%E9%80%BC%E5%B1%85%E7%99%BE%E5%91%8E%E5%BB%9A%E5%BB%81%E7%9B%B8%E9%80%A3-&d=Au6C6jYmoXJsWFOyr%2BboKPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=cdd27d37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20170320%2F2_488605_0%2F-N%E7%84%A1%E6%82%B2%E6%85%98%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C-%E8%80%81%E9%BC%A0%E5%85%A5%E5%B1%8B%E5%92%AC%E7%88%9B%E9%9B%BB%E7%B7%9A-%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%B6%E5%9B%9B%E5%8F%A3%E9%80%BC%E5%B1%85%E7%99%BE%E5%91%8E%E5%BB%9A%E5%BB%81%E7%9B%B8%E9%80%A3-&h=7e00ef72\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/時事要聞/article/20170320/2_488605_0/-N無悲慘世界-老鼠入屋咬爛電線-一家四口逼居百呎廚廁相連-</a></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n香港住屋問題愈來愈嚴重，上車難，租金又不斷上升。過往關愛基金為非公屋、非綜援的低收入住戶，提供俗稱「N無人士」的一次過生活津貼，令不少人士受惠，不過今年關愛基金突然取消項目，令受助人頓時失去援助。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170318/large/1489826458_fffb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170318%2Flarge%2F1489826458_fffb.jpg&h=c23d8625&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年領取四人家庭N無津貼13000元的梁女士，<span style=\"color: red;\">2006年隻身來港，丈夫與兒子其後再申請來港團聚</span>，一家四口居住於葵芳一個不足百呎的單位內，月租3100元。單位空間十分狹窄，放了一張上下格床，兩名兒子在上格床睡，兩夫婦則睡下格床。床旁邊是一個組合櫃，亦有獨立洗手間，但「廚廁」相連，衛生情況惡劣。 <br />\n<br />\n「我先生做地盤散工，我送兒子上學後才做散工，送貨，有時送單。」梁女士跟丈夫每月收入約二萬元，但由於工作不穩定，收入有多有少，「支出佔我和先生的人工百分之九十以上。」長子有智力殘障，不能自立，而幼子正讀小五，亦需要照顧，梁女士為了兩名兒子未能做全職工作。 <br />\n<br />\n生活困難，加上取消N無津貼，他們只能選擇租住較細較便宜的劏房，「非常擠逼，同時非常惡劣。近這大半年，蟑螂老鼠都有，日前才捉了兩隻老鼠，幾乎咬爛電線。」當然少不免會漏水，「漏水一定有，經常困擾自己的就是滲水問題。而且兩名兒子慢慢長大，少少私人空間都沒有。」 <br />\n<br />\n雖然津貼是一次過，但已對梁女士有很大幫助，「可以舒緩我每個月交租和日常生活開支的負擔。」"},{"pid":"77605465bcdaaf88645621337aa325512f85a650","tid":164812,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:42:11.000Z","msg":"慘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f99d644af6239a8d05ff52915e8994e630db61","tid":164812,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:45:40.000Z","msg":"中國咁多地唔去中國住，走黎香港逼都唔知做乜鳩"},{"pid":"c7097c939ba370cd56adeb28671e63587d8decb6","tid":164812,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:52:30.000Z","msg":"散工送貨有二萬/月？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n送乜鳩貨咁值錢？"},{"pid":"2d38155302eef497e7fc402cc79cb5a887588cd7","tid":164812,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:53:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>散工送貨有二萬/月？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n送乜鳩貨咁值錢？</blockquote><br />\n2人加埋"},{"pid":"b026825694c49713316d202ea4c1f7569da67b00","tid":164812,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:54:03.000Z","msg":"話時話，佢一開始係點隻身來港？無人無物點申請？"},{"pid":"c08b87cafc2fbf51d645cf885c98815a57562b9c","tid":164812,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:54:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>散工送貨有二萬/月？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n送乜鳩貨咁值錢？</blockquote><br />\n兩公婆加埋"},{"pid":"cf69f2091d9f4ce49dabbb8351211ec386dae36d","tid":164812,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:55:19.000Z","msg":"點解可以隻身來港? 又唔係團聚, 更加唔係投資, 佢用咩途徑拎居港權? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb78085a2ace2a582d2532d6cc33ae26cc0a9dca","tid":164812,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:55:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>散工送貨有二萬/月？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n送乜鳩貨咁值錢？</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">梁女士跟丈夫 每月收入約二萬元 </span> 呀文盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5cdbacdcb71ef0066b5be6f6f49a5878268aaee","tid":164812,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:56:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國咁多地唔去中國住，走黎香港逼都唔知做乜鳩</blockquote><br />\n香港可以扼綜緩唔使做丫麻"},{"pid":"aadac9e355c1b5a2828d70a40c389de9a292c05f","tid":164812,"uid":67266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T03:01:02.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲來講佢地唔算賤格架喇，起碼無拎公屋又有份正職，但落來香港咁過活，香港人又慘佢又慘，何必呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b6a490174c3615a68aa4ac428a1b4045ede72ca","tid":164812,"uid":60693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T03:01:36.000Z","msg":"大陸人真係仆街 死都要滾落黎"},{"pid":"d3d6d551d84070f891b9aad20c584c1e28f310cd","tid":164812,"uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T03:09:05.000Z","msg":"高質數移民"},{"pid":"f4dc943fbc2334355f68ab85e5fa9b20c9cfde63","tid":164812,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T03:22:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解可以隻身來港? 又唔係團聚, 更加唔係投資, 佢用咩途徑拎居港權? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nx2"},{"pid":"6dfaf9479a217d63116163b73b66f7ae6b8cfc1b","tid":164812,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T0